_sText:
This is the final (And I must say epic) version in the "Fy_coldworld" series. I've added another way to get from spawn to spawn. Of course I left the bouncy diving board, exept I added a sound for when you jump off.I've also added some cool lightning effects with lighting and some sounds. I also fixed the extreme lighting and turned it down a notch to make the other lights noticable. I ALSO made the skybox more reasonable to it's environment because I'm pretty sure there are no iceburgs on islands.(?) And I fixed the sniping positions from being hard to get in to.
Lastly, I fixed the old water to cool new water.
And again, bare with me this, is my 3rd map (Or the 3rd version of my first map)
ENJOY YOU SILLY LITTLE TROLLS!
